OL,5, Weather events, linked to a changing   
OL,6, climate, brought misery to millions    
OL,7, around the world in 2021 according to a
OL,8, new report.                            
OL,10,FThe study, from the charity Christian  
OL,11,FAid, identified 10 extreme events that 
OL,12,Feach caused more than $1.5bn of damage.
OL,14,FThe biggest financial impacts were from
OL,15,FHurricane Ida which hit the US in      
OL,16,FAugust and flooding in Europe in July. 
OL,18,FIn many poorer regions, floods and     
OL,19,Fstorms caused mass displacements of    
OL,20,Fpeople and severe suffering.           
